          608
        ]
      },
      {
        "parameters": {
          "jsCode": "const d = $input.first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    to: d.email,\n    subject: `Checking in — ${d.company}`,\n    html: `<p>Hi ${d.firstName || 'there'},</p><p>It's been a while since we last worked together, and I wanted to check in.</p><p>A lot has changed in the AI automation space since our last project. We've built some powerful new systems — from AI-powered lead qualification to automated client reporting — that could make a real difference for ${d.company}.</p><p>Would you be open to a quick 15-minute catch-up? I'd love to hear what's new on your end and share what we've been building.</p><p>${d.config.owner.calendarLink}</p><p>— John<br/>${d.config.owner.companyName}</p>`,\n    workflowName: 'SYS 05 — Referral & Reactivation Engine'\n  }\n}];"
        },
